   彼 の 仕事 の 成果 を 通じ て 「本 」 の 存在 理由 の 大きさ が 理解 できる の は 私 だけ だろ う か 。 ||| why not end the book . how did this become my fan takashi tachibana . amazed to see a collection of terrifying cats were housed in a building . and when we have confirmed that cats are put in this building that i read `` i 'm reading the same book says tachibana ~ '' what躍tta mind . tachibana is one of the largest in japan 's `` intellectual giant '' will . he and the raison d'etre of the way of working has been achieved by the actions of large amount of reading and logical thinking . here 's how to be good and not just the真似re his way , but i do not think that can be imitated and , through the results of his work `` books '' can understand the size of the reason for the existence of what my own .